Subject: Re: [T2] bus runs good, then bad

Steve,

Have him look for a restriction in the exhaust....debris and/or squeezed 
tubing somewhere.

If it was really bad, the engine would start, run fine for a few 
minutes/seconds and then die.

Cheers, dave

